<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <title>스프링부트 웹서비스</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <!--부트스트랩 css 추가-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/lib/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
<br/><br/>
<h2 class="text-center">검색어를 등록하시면 <p class="p-3 mb-2 bg-success text-white">NAVER 뉴스</p>검색결과를 주기적으로 저장하여 이미지로 보여드려요.(Ver.1)</h2>

<div class="col-md-12">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary mx-auto d-block" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#saveKeywordModal">검색 키워드 등록</button>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <!-- 목록 출력 영역 -->
    <table class="table table-horizontal table-bordered">
        <thead class="thead-strong">
        <tr>
            <th>검색 키워드</th>
            <th>키워드 등록 시간</th>
            <th>최근 이미지 생성 시간</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="tbody">
        {{#each keyword}}
            <tr>
                <td><a href="/keyword/{{id}}">{{name}}</a></td>
                <td>{{createdDate}}</td>
                <td>{{modifiedDate}}</td>
            </tr>
        {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <input type="hidden" id="keyword-length" value="{{keywordLength}}">
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="saveKeywordModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="saveKeywordLabel"
     aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="saveKeywordLabel">검색 키워드 등록</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <form>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="검색할 키워드를 입력하세요">
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">취소</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-save">등록</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<!--부트스트랩 js, jquery 추가-->
<script src="/js/lib/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/lib/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

<!--custom js 추가-->
<script src="/js/app/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>